Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shirakumo, pindahkan Midoriya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serangan kita tak mempan.\NPertahanan dia terlalu kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak seperti All For One,\Nilusiku tak mempan terhadap dia.
