Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.01,0:10:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mereka nyaris tidak bisa bergerak,\Ntapi mata mereka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mata mereka begitu gigih.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kesalahan besar memberi kekuatan itu\Npada pecundang tak berguna{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}yang hanya bisa melotot\Ntanpa bisa bergerak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku sudah mengerti, Midoriya.{\i0}
